pullRequest.title: VPC Manager service module
pullRequest.bodyText:
Launch vpc manager service and create common library (lib):

split vpc manager service from alcor
re-organize vpc manager directory structure
extract common library shared by multiple microservices
update kubernetes files in vpc manager

commit.message:
Merge pull request #1 from futurewei-cloud/master

Replace Redis with Apache Ignite for in memory cache and db (#129)
